org.universAAL.ontology.profile

Class UserProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.universAAL.middleware.rdf.Resource
      • org.universAAL.middleware.rdf.FinalizedResource
        • org.universAAL.middleware.owl.ManagedIndividual
          • org.universAAL.ontology.profile.Profile
            • org.universAAL.ontology.profile.UserProfile
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AssistedPersonProfile, CaregiverProfile

    public class UserProfile
extends Profile
    Ontological representation of the specific profile of an any person. Methods included in this class are the mandatory ones for representing an ontological concept in Java classes for universAAL. Usually it includes getters and setters for most of its properties.
    Author:
    Carsten Stockloew, Alvaro Fides, Peter Wolf
